10) pango-1.14.8-sinhala5.patch
http://bugzilla.gnome.org/show_bug.cgi?id=385321

The worst case expansion for Sinhala should be 4, not 3. e.g.
(kombuva)(dotted_circle)(aela-pilla)(al-lakuna). However, this
patch is only superficial because Pango doesn't appear to ever
use the worst case expansion value, unlike ICU.
